description: Welcome home to this expansive home at 120 W 7th St. #402 in the exciting West Side neighborhood of South Boston. With over 1600 square feet of living space this corner unit has sweeping views of the Boston skyline. This sun-drenched home has three exposures over 10 massive double windows, allowing for an abundance of natural light. The master suite is expansive and features multiple closets including an oversized walk-in as well as a spacious en-suite bathroom. The second bedroom is also king-sized currently able to accommodate a bedroom, playroom and office all in one. Third space/den area with TV could easily be the 3rd bedroom. With Brazilian hardwoods throughout, granite counters, SS appliances, surround sound & 1 deeded garage parking spot as well as an incredible 2,500 square foot common roof deck with two gas grills and amazing views of Boston. Just steps from the Broadway T stop, restaurants, retail, coffee shops, parks, and more!
